                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>For the text of the address delivered by President <persName
                        corresp="#p_TRUMANHS1">Truman</persName> in Groton, Connecticut, at the keel
                    laying of the U.S.S. <hi rend="italic">Nautilus</hi>, the first nuclear-powered
                    submarine, June 14, 1952, see <hi rend="italic">Public Papers</hi>
                    <pb facs="0168" n="982" xml:id="pg_982"/>
                    <hi rend="italic">of the Presidents of the United States: <persName
                            corresp="#p_TRUMANHS1">Harry S. Truman</persName>, 1952–53</hi>, pages
                    425–429.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
